title: Invisible but Invaluable
itunes:title: Invisible but Invaluable
description:
The prophet Elijah performed many great miracles, but behind the scenes, there was Elisha faithfully caring for his every need. Learn how to live each day helping others. As you make other people shine, God will make sure the right people will be there for you to help you shine and rise higher. Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love. To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
